# GreenGuard Implementation Plan

GreenGuard is a web application to detect greenwashing in corporate marketing text using Gemini 3 Pro.

## User Review Required
> [!IMPORTANT]
> The application requires a valid API key for Gemini 3 Pro (`GEMINI_API_KEY`). The user will need to provide this or set it in their environment. I will use a placeholder or check for the env var.

